tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE healthcare_outcomes_data (
    patient_id INT,
    patient_name VARCHAR(50),
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    treatment_type VARCHAR(20),
    outcome VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE PatientData (
  PatientID INT,
  Age INT,
  Gender VARCHAR(10),
  Race VARCHAR(20),
  Treatment VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE TreatmentOutcomes (
  OutcomeID INT,
  PatientID INT,
  Treatment VARCHAR(50),
  Outcome VARCHAR(50),
  OutcomeScore INT,
  OutcomeDate DATE
);

CREATE TABLE Treatments (
  treatment_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id UUID REFERENCES Patients(patient_id),
  treatment_name VARCHAR,
  dosage INT,
  outcome VARCHAR
);

CREATE TABLE Demographics (
  demo_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id UUID REFERENCES Patients(patient_id),
  income INT,
  education_level VARCHAR,
  insurance_type VARCHAR
);

CREATE TABLE patients (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  first_name TEXT,
  last_name TEXT,
  age INT,
  gender TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE treatments (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  treatment_name TEXT,
  effectiveness TEXT,
  side_effects TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE hospitals (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  hospital_name TEXT,
  location TEXT,
  rating FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE doctors (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  doctor_name TEXT,
  specialty TEXT,
  experience_years INT
)

CREATE TABLE outcomes (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT,
  treatment_id INT,
  hospital_id INT,
  doctor_id INT,
  outcome_result TEXT
)
